ations on how to stabilise and\nmanipulate DWs as well as skymionic structures in magnetic multilayers.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 16 Dec 2017 16:04:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 4 Jan 2018 13:10:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-11-06"}
