e present model is stable and accurate at\na wider temperature range. Lastly, our newly proposed model can be easily and\nreliably applied to various practical simulations and expected to obtain some\nmore interesting results.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 17 Dec 2017 09:34:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-12-19"}
