 in our recent work. Whereas inter-band absorption -- together with\nLandau damping -- is shown adverse to the instability, a dielectric brings it\ncloser to occurrence. One may even attain it in common plasmonic materials such\nas silver under not so tough conditions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 17 Dec 2017 12:49:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 26 Dec 2017 12:49:49 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 17 Jan 2018 09:57:05 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Sun, 22 Jul 2018 09:41:19 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Tue, 21 Aug 2018 10:30:39 GMT"},{"version":"v6","created":"Fri, 1 Feb 2019 13:57:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-05-02"}
